
# Dr. David Andai — Portfolio

Personal portfolio for Dr. David Andai, a physician-researcher working at the intersection of brain health, neuroscience, and machine learning. The site covers his research focus areas — brain health burden, brain health determinants, and brain capital — alongside his clinical experience, peer-reviewed publications, Neural Dome AI projects, skills and certifications, talks, awards, and affiliations including his MNeuroSc at UCT and MINDS 2026 scholarship.

Built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.
